ed directly. CLASSIFICATION for Tomorrow - The above are the current VA and NC classifications.These classifications are considered OFFICIAL in the calendar above at 5:00 p.m. for VA EST or EDT, and 6:00 p.m. for NC EST or EDT, and are considered ANTICIPATED prior to those times.- Virginia Non-Jurisdictional Customers: Tomorrow's OFFICIAL classification is available today only at 5:00 p.m. EST or EDT, as applicable, at 1-800-446-4877 or 1-800-768-2889.- North Carolina Customers: Tomorrow's OFFICIAL classification is provided above, today at 6:00 p.m. EST or EDT, as applicable.- Virginia Customers: Tomorrow's OFFICIAL"
